    <item>
      <title>Re: causes a bug in admin interface when not lo...</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/admin2pp/forum/general/causes_a_bug_in_admin_interface_when_not_logged_in/re_causes_a_bug_in_admin_interface_when_not_lo</link>
      <description>Hi Marko,&#13;
&#13;
&lt;i&gt;When this extension is enabled and you go to the admin interface without being logged in (the user/login page is presented), a lot of unneeded .js files are loaded.&lt;/i&gt;&#13;
&#13;
this is done on purpose. The idea is to asynchronously fill the browser's cache while the user is filling the login form (or trying to remember his password :-)) to speed up the admin interface page loadings.&#13;
&#13;
&lt;i&gt;Among them also the .js files for OE are loaded and one of them causes a "Request-URI too large" error response. On some servers this triggers security mechanisms that block access from the user's computer.&lt;/i&gt;&#13;
&#13;
yeah I noticed this issue too, as a workaround, you can remove the guilty JavaScript file from [PreloadSettings]/OEJavaScriptFiles[] array in admin2pp.ini&#13;
&#13;
Cheers</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Damien Pobel)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/admin2pp/forum/general/causes_a_bug_in_admin_interface_when_not_logged_in/re_causes_a_bug_in_admin_interface_when_not_lo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Sep 2011 14:55:24 +0000</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>causes a bug in admin interface when not logged in</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/admin2pp/forum/general/causes_a_bug_in_admin_interface_when_not_logged_in</link>
      <description>When this extension is enabled and you go to the admin interface without being logged in (the user/login page is presented), a lot of unneeded .js files are loaded.&#13;
Among them also the .js files for OE are loaded and one of them causes a "Request-URI too large" error response. On some servers this triggers security mechanisms that block access from the user's computer.&#13;
&#13;
This issue is also described here:&#13;
&#13;
http://issues.ez.no/IssueView.php?Id=18628</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Mavko Žmak - Žmale)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/admin2pp/forum/general/causes_a_bug_in_admin_interface_when_not_logged_in</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Sep 2011 09:18:13 +0000</pubDate>
