      <title>Re: A touch of details on this promising initia...</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/admin2pp/forum/general/a_touch_of_details_on_this_promising_initiative/re_a_touch_of_details_on_this_promising_initia2</link>
      <description>Hi there. about the calendar maybe you can take a look at the one provided by jquery UI [1]. I'm usign it for my custom extensions. As you probably know, the good thing about ui is that you can download only the components you need for your application, so maybe a "jquery ui for eZ Publish" can be provided with your extension. &#13;
&#13;
The "bad" thing about ui is that even you can download only the components you need, probably those components provides more functionality than you really need, an this could increase the javascript size innecesary. &#13;
&#13;
Just an idea. Thanks for your extension :). &#13;
&#13;
[1] http://www.jqueryui.com</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Carlos Revillo)</author>
